---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import HorizontalCard from "../components/HorizontalCard.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Areas of Expertise" sideBarActiveItemID="services">
  <div>
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold mb-5">Areas of Expertise</div>
  </div>

  <HorizontalCard
    title="AI Governance & Assurance"
    img="/ai_governance_layer.jpg"
    desc={`Designing practical governance systems for AI and ML products, including:
	•	governance architecture and decision rights
	•	documentation and transparency processes
	•	risk assessment frameworks
	•	scalable model oversight structures
	•	process design for compliance without bureaucracy

Approach: neutral, technical, and grounded in economic reasoning.`}
    url="#"
  />
  <div class="divider my-0"></div>
  <HorizontalCard
    title="Decision Systems & Decision Architecture"
    img="/decision_systems.jpg"
    desc={`Helping organizations build clear structures for high-stakes decisions:
	•	decision maps and logic frameworks
	•	structured thinking methodologies
	•	escalation, review, and feedback loops
	•	process clarity for ambiguous or complex environments
	•	integrating human judgment with analytical tools

Outcome: durable decision processes that scale beyond individuals.`}
    url="#"
  />
  <div class="divider my-0"></div>
  <HorizontalCard
    title="Pricing & Strategy Frameworks"
    img="/pricing_strategy.jpg"
    desc={`Focused on framework design, not operational pricing analytics or:
	•	pricing architecture and logic
	•	value-based pricing processes
	•	analytical strategy frameworks
	•	scenario design & structured evaluation methods

Designed for organizations that want repeatable logic, not one-off pricing recommendations.`}
    url="#"
  />
  <div class="divider my-0"></div>
  <HorizontalCard
    title="Forecasting & Economic Modelling"
    img="/economic_modeling.jpg"
    desc={`Credibility-enhancing and complementary:
	•	model design & validation logic
	•	forecasting frameworks
	•	policy or market analysis structures

Useful for clients needing analytical rigor embedded into governance or strategy work.`}
    url="#"
  />
</BaseLayout>
